{
  "texts": [
    "We hope to reach such a comparable amount as emerged with the release of the recent Capture-24 (∼ 2,500 hr data) [35] and BioBank (∼ 100,000 participants) [36] datasets, even if they include a reduced variety of sensors.",
    "Moreover, availability issues may still prevent free access to such data.",
    "Another area for improvement is that our work has been conducted on offline experiments, and the behavior of such models in real settings needs to be evaluated.",
    "We plan to investigate how these techniques can be applied with active learning [27].",
    "Finally, the study was restricted to three SSL techniques and two models."
  ]
}